  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Reports of Chaos activity on Hyades draw Ragnar Blackmane and the Space Wolves into a campaign already shadowed by Dark Angels secrecy. What should be a purge becomes an armed trust-crisis between two proud Chapters, each reading insult and ancient grievance into the other's every move while the true heretic enemy profits from the fracture. The old Russ-and-Lion rivalry threatens to drown the battlefield before Ragnar can force anyone to look at the real war. A straight-edged action novel built around brotherhood curdling into suspicion.",
